Package: SCIRA
Type: Package
Title: Single Cell Inference of Regulatory Activity
Description: SCIRA (Single Cell Inference of Regulatory Activity) is such a hybrid approach which uses the inferred predicted targets (or "regulon") of a given transcription factor from bulk data to infer its regulatory activity in each single cell.
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2019-07-26
Author: Ning Wang [aut, cre],
  Andrew Teschendorff [aut]
Maintainer: Ning Wang <wangning@picb.ac.cn>
License: GPL-3
